author: Xbox
description:
The digital version of the 2022 Golden Geek Best Board Game Expansion Nominee is now available on Xbox Series X|S and Xbox One!

Wingspan: Asia Expansion will take you on a journey through eclectic, breathtaking bird sanctuaries. Prepare to explore a world of colorful, diverse, and intriguing birds that bring new strategies, powers, and challenges. With this expansion, you’ll encounter unique birds and bonus cards, discover the beauty of region-inspired backgrounds, and add new player portraits that immerse you in the enchanting atmosphere of Asia.
